  "detailed_description": "- ASMR Journey!<br>She shouted, opening the door to her bookstore in the corner of living room.<br>It was the little witch who sell magic books.<br>At hand was his new volume, with a peculiar name. But what journey would that be? Maybe we all need to know!<br><br><br>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439800/extras/aff4c51f67534d3b26eef5a6a127abc7.avif?t=1608252809\" width=388 height=224 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">                                                                                                                                 <li> 5 peaceful and serene environments;<br></li><li> 3 different levels of difficulty;<br></li><li> Immersive soundtrack with relaxing ambient sounds;<br></li><li> A little story of magic and peace.</li></ul><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Zoom the scene;<br></li><li> Highlight border pieces;<br></li><li> Shuffle the remaining pieces;<br></li><li> Preview the image complete.</li></ul><br>A creative and serene mind is the magic for an eternal life.<br><br>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439800/extras/2e1054503b193be2933342ae1957a684.avif?t=1608252809\" width=200 height=449 /></span>",
